T10:39:45.000Z","msg":"我知呢個時候講特狗選舉會俾人勁屌，又話人血饅頭又話唔理理大學生，但作為一直支持學生嘅on9和理非嘅廢中，想同大家講中共唸嘢永遠Think ahead幾年，前線勇武當然繼續要撐，但和理非都要做嘢。<br />\n廢話少講，自己睇：(Sorry 剩係搵到殘體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.rfi.fr/cn/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD/20191125-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%8C%BA%E8%AE%AE%E4%BC%9A%E9%80%89%E4%B8%BE%E7%8A%B9%E5%A6%82%E6%B5%B7%E5%95%B8%E5%8F%8D%E5%AF%B9%E6%B4%BE%E5%A4%A7%E8%83%9C%E5%9C%A8%E6%9C%9B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfi.fr%2Fcn%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259B%25BD%2F20191125-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%258C%25BA%25E8%25AE%25AE%25E4%25BC%259A%25E9%2580%2589%25E4%25B8%25BE%25E7%258A%25B9%25E5%25A6%2582%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E5%2595%25B8%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%25AF%25B9%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%2583%259C%25E5%259C%25A8%25E6%259C%259B&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJuxpY9ERoCMedVnvBBvIoB8%3D&h=9a68a4ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.rfi.fr/cn/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD/20191125-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%8C%BA%E8%AE%AE%E4%BC%9A%E9%80%89%E4%B8%BE%E7%8A%B9%E5%A6%82%E6%B5%B7%E5%95%B8%E5%8F%8D%E5%AF%B9%E6%B4%BE%E5%A4%A7%E8%83%9C%E5%9C%A8%E6%9C%9B</a><br />\n<br />\n在香港特首選舉委員會1200個席位中，有117個席位，由區議員互選產生，採全票制。過往建制派主導區議會之下，這些選委席位都由建制包辦。民主派在上屆選委會有325席，如果這次區選過半繼而盡攬117個特首選委席位，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">民主派將坐擁約440席，佔1200人組成的選委會三分之一</span></span></strong>，足以左右大局。<br />\n<br />\n假設非建制攞到特首選委442 (325+117)席，即係話<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>只要攞多159票(601-442)，特首都有得你做!</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n你話中央會DQ，係。今次好多人話今次區選都無用，但喺國際戰線上show到俾人睇香港人已經發聲，係deserve有普選，同時亦令勇武有更多民意支持，可以去盡D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。如果選委選到個非建制特首出嚟然後老共DQ，國際會更同情港人，更多國家會行HK Human Rights and Democracy Act制裁中共，對我地百利而無一害。<br />\n<br />\n好多人話商界點會幫我地，但商界都有好多人暗中不滿中共，個問題係你要地產黨，定要共產黨：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/commentaries/kl/com-12122016075042.html?encoding=traditional\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fcantonese%2Fcommentaries%2Fkl%2Fcom-12122016075042.html%3Fencoding%3Dtraditional&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJuxpY9ERoCMedVnvBBvIoB8%3D&h=a7ffe90f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/commentaries/kl/com-12122016075042.html?encoding=traditional</a><br />\n<br />\n好啦，就當我地要攞商界嘅票，個問題係要分析邊D人係深紅，邊D人有機會倒戈。<br />\n2017特首選舉1194個選委<br />\n林奠：580提名, 777票<br />\n薯片：165提名，365票<br />\n胡國興：180提名，21票<br />\n<br />\n2012特首選舉1193名選委<br />\n唐唐：390提名，285票<br />\nCY：305提名，689票<br />\nAV仁：188提名，76票<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/2017%E5%B9%B4%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%89%B9%E5%88%A5%E8%A1%8C%E6%94%BF%E5%8D%80%E8%A1%8C%E6%94%BF%E9%95%B7%E5%AE%98%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F2017%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%2589%25B9%25E5%2588%25A5%25E8%25A1%258C%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25A1%258C%25E6%2594%25BF%25E9%2595%25B7%25E5%25AE%2598%25E9%2581%25B8%25E8%2588%2589&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJuxpY9ERoCMedVnvBBvIoB8%3D&h=10120ed4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/2017%E5%B9%B4%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%89%B9%E5%88%A5%E8%A1%8C%E6%94%BF%E5%8D%80%E8%A1%8C%E6%94%BF%E9%95%B7%E5%AE%98%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/2012%E5%B9%B4%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%89%B9%E5%88%A5%E8%A1%8C%E6%94%BF%E5%8D%80%E8%A1%8C%E6%94%BF%E9%95%B7%E5%AE%98%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F2012%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%2589%25B9%25E5%2588%25A5%25E8%25A1%258C%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25A1%258C%25E6%2594%25BF%25E9%2595%25B7%25E5%25AE%2598%25E9%2581%25B8%25E8%2588%2589&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJuxpY9ERoCMedVnvBBvIoB8%3D&h=77c053d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/2012%E5%B9%B4%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%89%B9%E5%88%A5%E8%A1%8C%E6%94%BF%E5%8D%80%E8%A1%8C%E6%94%BF%E9%95%B7%E5%AE%98%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/daily/article/20170302/19944058\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20170302%2F19944058&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJuxpY9ERoCMedVnvBBvIoB8%3D&h=8a5621d4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20170302%2F19944058&h=152638f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/daily/article/20170302/19944058</a><br />\n<br />\n2017年薯片+胡官386票，當中有泛民投佢地，由於係暗票所以無人知<br />\n2012年唐唐有285票，肯定係全部建制，<br />\n假設唐營人數基本上無變，即係有285票係有機會唔聽中央支笛。未來幾年要試下lobby/拉籠呢班人，試圖令佢地當中一半左右可以倒戈，由於係暗票，中央都未必吹得佢漲。<br />\n<br />\n既然可以飛到世界各地lobby議員，點解唔可以近近地lobby商界呢？<br />\n<br />\n唐唐提名名單：<br />\n<a href=\"http://paper.wenweipo.com/2012/02/22/HK1202220018.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpaper.wenweipo.com%2F2012%2F02%2F22%2FHK1202220018.htm&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJuxpY9ERoCMedVnvBBvIoB8%3D&h=564dc960\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://paper.wenweipo.com/2012/02/22/HK1202220018.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n薯片提名名單：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%89%B9%E9%A6%96%E9%81%B8%E8%88%892017/74284/%E7%89%B9%E9%A6%96%E9%81%B8%E6%88%B0-%E6%9B%BE%E4%BF%8A%E8%8F%AF%E6%8F%90%E5%90%8D%E5%90%8D%E5%96%AE%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89-%E8%83%A1%E6%96%87%E6%96%B0-%E7%88%BE%E5%86%AC%E9%99%9E%E5%81%9A-%E8%96%AF%E7%B2%89\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%2589%25B9%25E9%25A6%2596%25E9%2581%25B8%25E8%2588%25892017%2F74284%2F%25E7%2589%25B9%25E9%25A6%2596%25E9%2581%25B8%25E6%2588%25B0-%25E6%259B%25BE%25E4%25BF%258A%25E8%258F%25AF%25E6%258F%2590%25E5%2590%258D%25E5%2590%258D%25E5%2596%25AE%25E6%259B%259D%25E5%2585%2589-%25E8%2583%25A1%25E6%2596%2587%25E6%2596%25B0-%25E7%2588%25BE%25E5%2586%25AC%25E9%2599%259E%25E5%2581%259A-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E7%25B2%2589&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJuxpY9ERoCMedVnvBBvIoB8%3D&h=87727a47\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%89%B9%E9%A6%96%E9%81%B8%E8%88%892017/74284/%E7%89%B9%E9%A6%96%E9%81%B8%E6%88%B0-%E6%9B%BE%E4%BF%8A%E8%8F%AF%E6%8F%90%E5%90%8D%E5%90%8D%E5%96%AE%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89-%E8%83%A1%E6%96%87%E6%96%B0-%E7%88%BE%E5%86%AC%E9%99%9E%E5%81%9A-%E8%96%AF%E7%B2%89</a><br />\n<br />\n胡官提名名單：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%89%B9%E9%A6%96%E9%81%B8%E8%88%892017/74588/%E7%89%B9%E9%A6%96%E9%81%B8%E6%88%B0-%E8%83%A1%E5%9C%8B%E8%88%88%E6%8C%BE180%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E6%B4%BE%E6%8F%90%E5%90%8D%E5%A0%B1%E5%90%8D-%E5%8A%9B%E9%98%BB%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E7%95%B6%E9%81%B8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%2589%25B9%25E9%25A6%2596%25E9%2581%25B8%25E8%2588%25892017%2F74588%2F%25E7%2589%25B9%25E9%25A6%2596%25E9%2581%25B8%25E6%2588%25B0-%25E8%2583%25A1%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%2588%2588%25E6%258C%25BE180%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E6%258F%2590%25E5%2590%258D%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%2590%258D-%25E5%258A%259B%25E9%2598%25BB%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E7%2595%25B6%25E9%2581%25B8&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJuxpY9ERoCMedVnvBBvIoB8%3D&h=06e8a847\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%89%B9%E9%A6%96%E9%81%B8%E8%88%892017/74588/%E7%89%B9%E9%A6%96%E9%81%B8%E6%88%B0-%E8%83%A1%E5%9C%8B%E8%88%88%E6%8C%BE180%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E6%B4%BE%E6%8F%90%E5%90%8D%E5%A0%B1%E5%90%8D-%E5%8A%9B%E9%98%BB%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E7%95%B6%E9%81%B8</a><br />\n<br />\n寫住咁多先，希望可以拋磚引玉。佢地選委最怕俾人開名，希望有巴打可以開條戰線暗中聯絡商界，例如思言財雋之類，多謝大家。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T10:52:22.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a54febf0ba90d6deead007a9d66e6467eb0b4c6a","tid":1754820,"uid":51349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T11:00:36.000Z","msg":"你話中央會DQ，係。今次好多人話今次區選都無用，但喺國際戰線上show到俾人睇香港人已經發聲，係deserve有普選，同時亦令勇武有更多民意支持，可以去盡D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。如果選委選到個非建制特首出嚟然後老共DQ，國際會更同情港人，更多國家會行HK Human Rights and Democracy Act制裁中共，對我地百利而無一害。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢度好同意,D人係咁講制度冇用 係咁講重諗住參加 增加合法性既痴線說話<br />\n鬼唔知未必有用咩,咁唔係你杯葛個選舉 人地就唔做嘛, 短期內都睇唔到大陸會一下比你普選<br />\n係制度下反抗 都係一種辦法,佢真係DQ 咪更加影響輿論<br />\n又唔係你唔參加 對面就唔派條友出黎<br />\n<br />\n計689 同777票 係鐵票 ,呢117票都會好大影響力 <br />\n商界一定有覺得被批鬥既情況出現,至於拉唔拉攏到就真係難講"},{"pid":"66e18eb3974c65ad64c838abe553e313209b120d","tid":1754820,"uid":293417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T11:02:05.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"241c4523396f0cd45240f9d96fae5b46052eeaa2","tid":1754820,"uid":293417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66e18eb3974c65ad64c838abe553e313209b120d","tid":1754820,"uid":293417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T11:02:05.000Z","msg":"Pish"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T11:06:07.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"b4a73668b9734432e1b4480cc606632981923c7d","tid":1754820,"uid":293417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"241c4523396f0cd45240f9d96fae5b46052eeaa2","tid":1754820,"uid":293417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66e18eb3974c65ad64c838abe553e313209b120d","tid":1754820,"uid":293417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T11:02:05.000Z","msg":"Pish"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T11:06:07.000Z","msg":"Pish"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T11:33:23.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"6b6e654c68ae8b12e2fc6731ea04126b76198645","tid":1754820,"uid":293417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T12:01:17.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"450926a64d228630c2f662d63c229932dc98eb6a","tid":1754820,"uid":293417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T12:03:50.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8a83fa2b12a885076d64f3f688392dfcda5e2f17","tid":1754820,"uid":293417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T12:29:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jcW7vrb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjcW7vrb.png&h=3b8e0bb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XQ6CSEx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXQ6CSEx.png&h=e5409ab5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iMQL1xS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiMQL1xS.png&h=9c66dcdf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b21e5c9cf415856a24feabb5b63d0e82a8384aa9","tid":1754820,"uid":293417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T15:57:02.000Z","msg":"Pish"}]}